		id: "0000000000208001"
		x: -2.0d
		y: 0.0d
		title: "About the Shop"
		icon: {id: "minecraft:emerald", Count: 1b}
		description: ["The Shop converts Coins earned through Main Progression quest rewards into useful materials, shortcuts, and utility items. Coins are awarded for major milestones — hull crafts, boss kills, multiblock assemblies, and significant progression gates — and accumulate passively as you play. Every repeatable purchase here can be completed as many times as your Coin balance allows.", "Coins are awarded throughout the Main Progression chapters. Check your quest reward history if you are unsure of your balance. The Shop is not a cheat shortcut — everything available here can also be obtained through normal play. The Shop converts accumulated Coin reward into time savings when a specific material is blocking progress and grinding it manually is the slower path."]
		tasks: [{
			id: "0000000000208002"
			type: "checkmark"
			title: "Read about the Shop"
		}]
		rewards: [{
			id: "0000000000208003"
			type: "item"
			item: {id: "kubejs:coin", Count: 2b}
		}]
	}, {
