		x: 0.0d
		y: -4.0d
		title: "Steel Bundle"
		icon: {id: "gtceu:steel_ingot", Count: 1b}
		description: ["A bundle of 32 Steel Ingots for 2 Coins. Steel is the backbone of the LV-MV tier — machine housings, frames, pipes, and conveyors all require it in volume. If your steel production is behind your circuit assembly pace, buy time here."]
